Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I heard a sorrowful call... like none I'd ever heard... in the icy air.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, there it is again... Over that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A human voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rust...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It stopped...
